WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:05.766
I carved the words on the gold lock

2
00:00:06.066 --> 00:00:08.600
Your one has my name engraved on it.

3
00:00:08.966 --> 00:00:10.666
As long as there is a gold lock

4
00:00:10.900 --> 00:00:12.466
Wherever you are

5
00:00:12.566 --> 00:00:14.966
Mom will find you and reunite with you

6
00:00:16.466 --> 00:00:17.500
Don't talk nonsense

7
00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:19.500
He wants to take my place

8
00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:22.500
You've got to get him out of the house. Enough

9
00:00:23.866 --> 00:00:26.166
You all say that the golden lock belongs to you

10
00:00:26.166 --> 00:00:28.000
Then tell me where he came from

11
00:00:28.133 --> 00:00:29.433
Prove it yourself

12
00:00:30.133 --> 00:00:33.066
Oops, Shen Mei didn't mention this.

13
00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:34.866
Where am I going?

14
00:00:35.566 --> 00:00:37.700
Mom, you start first

15
00:00:38.866 --> 00:00:40.466
20 years have passed

16
00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:43.033
Mom has been through too much in Xiaodao Village

17
00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:46.166
Some things I really can't remember

18
00:00:48.566 --> 00:00:50.366
Shen Gui, you said

19
00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:54.200
This was 20 years ago.

20
00:00:54.266 --> 00:00:56.400
Mom used all her savings

21
00:00:56.400 --> 00:00:58.300
Here's your birthday present.

22
00:00:58.900 --> 00:01:01.433
But I haven't had time to celebrate your birthday yet.

23
00:01:01.566 --> 00:01:04.066
I was sold by your grandfather

24
00:01:05.666 --> 00:01:08.033
Ah yes, I suddenly remembered

25
00:01:08.533 --> 00:01:10.733
This is my birthday present for you.

26
00:01:10.733 --> 00:01:11.366
I didn't expect it.

27
00:01:11.366 --> 00:01:14.100
This matter was overheard by that bitch Shen Mei

28
00:01:15.533 --> 00:01:17.166
It's not my mom at all

29
00:01:18.066 --> 00:01:19.100
That's not true.

30
00:01:19.133 --> 00:01:20.900
I just forgot for a while

31
00:01:20.900 --> 00:01:22.133
You must believe me.

32
00:01:22.133 --> 00:01:23.300
I am your mother

33
00:01:24.066 --> 00:01:24.766
Don't you dare?

34
00:01:24.766 --> 00:01:25.766
Dare to lie

